    <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520"> 
      <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head> 
      <p>Films and videos of Cornell University football games.</p> 
      <p>Also, "The Big Red Machine: Exciting play-by-play highlights of Cornell's 1971 Ivy League Championship season narrated by Jay Levine."</p>
      <p>Digitization of films can be arranged if requested.</p> 
      
    </scopecontent> 
