    <relatedmaterial> 
      <head id="a5">RELATED MATERIALS</head> 
      <p>Some films labeled "highlights" may refer to a single game.</p> 
      <p>University of Pennsylvania Archives has film of all Penn-Cornell
        games.</p> 
      <p>See also Cornell University Football Game Highlights, #40-2-1000, for some 1950 and 1951 reels. Also Hunter Ripley Rawlings Papers, #3-13-2843, for 1991 highlights.</p> 
      <p>See also Howard Schuck papers, #37-5-2629, for more information on the team, particularly on the Ohio game of 1939.</p> 
      <p>See also Cornell University Museum Items, #47-7-1948.</p>
      <p>See also Big Red Band Records, #37-6-3112.</p>
      <p>See also Football Miscellany, #37-5-3981.</p>
      <p>Ernest William Schoder papers, #16-4-1156 for some 1929-1930 games.</p>
    </relatedmaterial> 
